      IBooleanLiteral IBooleanLiteral.complement()
      Constructs a new IBooleanLiteral with the same internal IBooleanVariable but with opposite barring; that is, if this IBooleanLiteral is barred, its complement will be unbarred, if not then its complement will be barred.
